{"tid":2078213,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"80多年歷史 Olympus宣布出售數碼相機等映像業務 智能電話普及致數碼相機銷量低迷","createTime":"2020-06-25T01:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T05:47:23.000Z","uid":66260,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b69a9c5b4460d88c0f4ea446429e46e79a11b8c5","tid":2078213,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/olympus-sell-cam-business/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Folympus-sell-cam-business%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=4256d603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/olympus-sell-cam-business/</a><br />\n<br />\nBy LikeJapan 編輯部 / 2020-06-25<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本著名相機品牌Olympus在24日宣布，將於九月把包括相機在內的影像事業一概出售予私募投資基金「日本產業夥伴」。Olympus自1936年開始研發相機鏡頭，發展相機事業至今已有八十多年歷史，近年推出的「OM―D」和「PEN」等無反相機系列也為品牌累積了不少人氣。<br />\n<br />\n八十多年歷史不敵智能電話的普及化<br />\n<br />\n隨著智能電話在2010年代推出，數碼相機的銷量從2010年的1.2億部急跌至去年的1521萬部，市場持續萎縮，Olympus的影像事業截至去年也已經連續三個財政年度錄得赤字。為了止血，公司決定出售影像事業，將資源集中在發展屬於其強項的醫療事業上。<br />\n<br />\n 80多年歷史 Olympus宣布出售數碼相機等映像業務 智能電話普及致數碼相機銷量低迷<br />\n&copy; Olympus Corporation. All Rights Reserved.<br />\n<br />\n除了做相機鏡頭　也做醫療用內視鏡<br />\n<br />\nOlympus在1919年創業時其實是一間顯微鏡公司，後來公司分別將該技術應用於發展相機事業和醫療事業上，而醫療事業上的應用又以內視鏡為主。據其網頁所指，Olympus在1952年研發了世界第一個胃部內視鏡，至今其消化系統內視鏡（圖）擁有世界市場近七成市佔率。<br />\n<br />\n雖然Olympus出售了相機事業，不過之後就可以將資源更有效地運用在醫療技術上，造福人群。而且出售也不代表品牌會從此絕跡於相機市場，影像事業以後將會交給由投資基金擁有的新公司管理，希望未來還能看見他們承傳Olympus八十多年的經驗，繼續推出高質素的好相機！<br />\n<br />\n 80多年歷史 Olympus宣布出售數碼相機等映像業務 智能電話普及致數碼相機銷量低迷<br />\n&copy; Olympus Corporation. All Rights Reserved.<br />\n參考資料來源：<br />\n<br />\n朝日新聞、NHK、Olympus官方網站<br />\n<br />\n人生第一部dc仔就係Olympus<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3e0a7ddf05538a09e930453c1f42c4762eee37","tid":2078213,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1268180bcb658ece1a73cd3bbe9bb03ef37d586","tid":2078213,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"支那出手了"},{"pid":"3f55f8615ba3bf66aebeaa99314f4a44ce279e47","tid":2078213,"uid":115082,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"上年買左部相機都係佢 買過2部<br />\n去旅行細細部 影出黎色又幾好 外型又靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5f422d4ecdb57e7d4c9ea6868004a0d8d6685f","tid":2078213,"uid":123905,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"當年minolta賣畀sony，而家sony相機幾強大"},{"pid":"880d375f89f57080b43ffbcebc9014f853bbaf5e","tid":2078213,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:13:21.000Z","msg":"下？？？"},{"pid":"cecd49604ad43b5f4a53ced3af7c49c318ae7e7e","tid":2078213,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"日本產業夥伴咩背景"},{"pid":"b249f1f167426955175705dab32e6e22307f1a46","tid":2078213,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"人生第一部單反"},{"pid":"ca21479f41c2946479daa63d883f7b08ae1ee5be","tid":2078213,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0fc11773cd3be96b6bb45c6fe67b9685de2fe24","tid":2078213,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d135829504c8b7172c0a5543101b5cb023f18760","tid":2078213,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"唔見牌子賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賴啦賴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgm